reinsurance</link> industry. <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2214%22])">14</ref> <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2215%22])">15</ref> By 2004 the companies Jones co-founded merged into a single company, <company wordnetid="108058098" confidence="0.8">
